        <h3>Sofya Ignatyeva - Secretary, Biology</h3>
        <p>Hello everyone! My name is Sofya and I am a biology major with aspirations to work hands on in the medical field as a physician. I think it is necessary to break stereotypes of woman not being able to take control and lead the way in medicine . In my free time I love to work out and travel whenever there is time. I also work in a private medical office and I try my best to assist and get a look at the medical field to learn what needs to be adapted and changed for the greater good. I’m so glad to meet everyone and hopefully we can all make a change!</p>
